import {Link, useNavigate} from "react-router-dom"; import {useDispatch, useSelector} from "react-redux"; import {useEffect} from "react"; import {login} from "../services/userService"; import {Field, Form, Formik} from "formik"; import "./Login.css" export default function Login() { const dispatch = useDispatch(); const navigate = useNavigate(); const handleLogin = async (values) => { let a = await dispatch(login(values)) console.log('a', a.payload.data.message) if (a.payload.data.message.token === "User is not exist") { alert("dang nhap ko thanh cong") navigate("/") } else if (a.payload.data.message.token === "Password is wrong") { alert("sai mk") navigate("/") } else { await dispatch(login(values)) navigate("/home") } } return (
{ handleLogin(values).then() }}>
) }
